Wealth is more than money!

Wealthy people have a harmony between these four things:

Spirituality
Emotional Intelligence 
Finances 
Relationship 

When you have one missing you will have to compensate the with the others. If you have two missing, your table won’t be able to stand!

You can’t have true wealth without making sure your 4 pillars intact!

Confidence and discipline are directly connected to what your intentions were at the beginning. You can’t have confidence and be disciplined or some thing if your intentions for that thing was wrong to start with.

so every time someone asked me how do you keep going and how do you stay disciplined when things get tough. 
I told them because my heart is in the right place when it came to whatever I was doing. And then I asked him what is keeping you from being disciplined? The first thing I always tell them to do is check their heart.

node.text:
As we all are being forced to catch up to the digital age we are being bombarded by companies built by people who don’t relate to our struggles!

As entrepreneurs we usually don’t have any experience in coding and web design  or anything really dealing with technology!

But as we see we are all being forced to dive head first into these shark infested waters! Usually being forced to barely stay afloat on a life raft built on a bunch or random companies! We try to jumble it all together not really knowing how it’s working together but it works lol! 

We decided to build a technology for those like me aren’t tech savvy but know how to drag and drop! We combined all of the functionality and resources the “top companies” claimed to have and put them in one place! Then we made it user friendly! 

BizCo builder can literally host your courses, host your landing pages, create your e-commerce store, and create funnels! Sits an entrepreneurs greatest tool for online business!

node.text:
Here is why! If someone sees and ad for a product and they decide to click the link. They are doing so looking to purchase the product they saw. Why send them to the full site to get lost trying to find that one thing that got them interested in the first place!

You want to close the sale first! Once they get to the check out that’s when you offer them a complimentary product to the first product. If they don’t take that offer your funnel will have another product that could go alongside it to also offer. But, don’t stop the first sale by having them drowned in a sea of other products and pages!

node.text:
Had I not been introduced to the world by my brother @brotherbenx I would still probably be just doing insurance with my little team and be doing perfectly fine! 

But God wanted my work to touch the masses even if I could physically get to them! What other way do you know that could make that possible other than jumping online? With the click of a button I can be in front of millions! Do you know how many doors I would have had to knock on to reach just 1 million people had I not gotten online?

If you take a step back and see where people spend majority of their time it’s on their phone online! So if you want to get their attention meet them where they are! 

If you need help transferring your business to the online market make sure to text, “BIZCO” to 281-524-3973 for more information and daily business game!

node.title: In today’s world your business has to have an online presence!

node.text:
People want my fruit but they don’t want the darkness that comes with my roots. 

What you see in the light will always be a reflection of what’s done in the dark. 

So if no on sees you keep working.
No one understands you keep working.
No one celebrates you keep working.

In short, God always rewards the diligent worker, especially if they are willing to work regardless of sunlight. 

I love you 

Dr. Jake Tayler Jacobs

🎶- @cevenimperial

node.title: It’s the darkness that made me.

It’s really mind boggling that the brokest people always know how to make money right! But if that’s the case why can’t it be seen in your life? 

My favorite books says, “a poor mans words are not heard they are despised.”

Lol even I had fallen victim to that mindset when i was broke! Going up against a millionaire while not even having $1k to my name! 

We need to learn to to listen, and stop talking all the time. 

#Text “BIZCO” to 281-524-3973 if you want wealth advise from someone who actually has real applicable advice!

node.text:
You can only change your life when you decide to take control of your life. If you don’t like what you see, you have all the power to change it! 

I began not to like what I was seeing so I reinvented myself. I molded myself into the Dr. Jake Tayler Jacobs you see today! 

Change simply requires you take control and make it happen. No excuses, more solutions!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Dr. Jake Tayler Jacobs on August 10, 2021. May be a Twitter screenshot of text that says 'Dr. Jake Tayler Jacobs @drjaketayler What people call impossible, I call possible. We will become a billion dollar debt free company, with NO SEED RAISING to our IPO. PRIOR God is in the proving business, and we will prove that customer acquisition is more important than "raising money" Nothing less than a BILL!'.

node.text:
What I’ve learned on this journey is the power of belief! 

Are we debt free ? YES 
Have we been funded by investors ? NO
Do we operate based on man’s standards? HELL NO. 

People told me it was impossible to build a company without debt.. we proved that was a lie. 

People told me we needed investors, we proved that was a lie. 

People said it would be hard to find talented minorities to come and work with the company, we also proved that was a lie. 

We have already become one of the few EVER billion dollar debt free companies. Time just has to catch up.

node.text:
Wealth is more than money!

Wealthy people have a harmony between these four things:

Spirituality
Emotional Intelligence 
Finances 
Relationship 

When you have one missing you will have to compensate the with the others. If you have two missing, your table won’t be able to stand!

You can’t have true wealth without making sure your 4 pillars intact!

#Text “BIZCO” to 281-524-3973 for more information and daily business game!

node.text:
The reason why you can’t stay disciplined is, your only goal is money. 
Money comes and goes! It’s a flow / transfer of value. But once you get the money then what will push you? What will keep you going!

There needs to be a mission, a purpose that fuels you. Something that is bigger than you. Something you can’t complete on your own! 

When you connect your life to a mission the discipline seems easier. Because you know what you are doing affects more than you.

#Text “BIZCO” to 281-524-3973 for more information and daily business game!

Confidence and discipline are directly connected to what your intentions were at the beginning. You can’t have confidence and be disciplined or some thing if your intentions for that thing was wrong to start with.

so every time someone asked me how do you keep going and how do you stay disciplined when things get tough. 
I told them because my heart is in the right place when it came to whatever I was doing. And then I asked him what is keeping you from being disciplined? The first thing I always tell them to do is check their heart.
